metadata.name: The Unfolding
metadata.description:
In the end, only three things matter;
How much you loved,
How gently you lived, and
how gracefully you let go of things not meant for you

This is what makes unfolding the divine feminine energy very significant within each and every one of us. Itâ€™s nature is to be loving, gentle and graceful no matter what life throws at it.
